---
// Infra widget — "spec sheet" layout (uniform label/value lines, robust).
// Narrative: provisioning (GitOps) → access (edge) → services → resilience.
// Reality (01-Homelab repo): all guests on pve02; resilience = PBS + restic
// offsite + IaC replayable from git. NetBox dropped (OOS/decommission per planning).
---

<section id="infra">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head"><h2>Infrastructure</h2><div class="rule"></div></div>
    <p class="sec-intro">
      Mon homelab, le terrain où je teste tout. Il est provisionné entièrement
      en code, exposé via une gateway VPS sans ouvrir un seul port à la maison, et conçu pour repartir
      depuis git après une panne, grâce à des backups que je teste vraiment.
    </p>

    <div class="infra-panel">
      <div class="infra-bar">
        <span class="ib-title">homelab.topology</span>
        <span class="ib-iac">IaC · repo privé</span>
      </div>

      <!-- build -->
      <div class="grp">
        <div class="line">
          <span class="k">provisioning</span>
          <span class="v">git push <i>→</i> Terraform + Ansible <i>→</i> Proxmox</span>
        </div>
        <div class="line">
          <span class="k">accès</span>
          <span class="v">internet <i>→</i> VPS Gateway <i>→</i> pve02 <span class="muted">· 13 LXC en IaC</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="line">
          <span class="k"></span>
          <span class="v muted">Caddy · Tailscale · Pocket ID · <b>0 port ouvert à la maison</b></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- services -->
      <div class="grp">
        <div class="line"><span class="k">edge &amp; sécurité</span><span class="v">Caddy · Tailscale · Pocket ID · AdGuard</span></div>
        <div class="line"><span class="k">observabilité</span><span class="v">Grafana · Prometheus · Loki · Uptime Kuma</span></div>
        <div class="line"><span class="k">apps</span><span class="v">Immich · Homepage · Paperless <span class="muted">· +3</span></span></div>
      </div>

      <!-- resilience -->
      <div class="grp resil">
        <div class="line">
          <span class="k"><span class="dot"></span>résilience</span>
          <span class="v"><b>PBS</b> local + <b>restic</b> offsite — 3-2-1 <em>restaurée-testée</em></span>
        </div>
        <div class="line">
          <span class="k"></span>
          <span class="v">infra <b>rejouable depuis Git</b> <span class="muted">— si le nœud tombe, je la rejoue</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* bande sombre pleine largeur — casse le bloc beige + renforce l'identité infra */
  #infra {
    padding: 76px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(170deg, var(--sidebar) 0%, var(--column) 100%);
  }
  #infra .sec-head h2 { color: var(--marble); }
  #infra .sec-head h2::before { color: var(--gold); }
  #infra .sec-intro { color: var(--marble-dark); opacity: .92; }

  .infra-panel {
    border: 1px solid #ffffff1f; border-radius: var(--r-panel);
    background: #241f19;
    overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(30,26,21,.28);
  }

  /* title bar — barre de fenêtre terminal */
  .infra-bar {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 11px 18px;
    background: #2a2520;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #00000040;
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  .ib-title { color: var(--marble-dark); opacity: .8; }
  .ib-iac { color: var(--gold); font-size: 11.5px; }
  .ib-iac em { font-style: normal; color: var(--marble-dark); opacity: .55; }

  /* groups separated by dividers */
  .grp { padding: 13px 18px; }
  .grp + .grp { border-top: 1px solid #ffffff14; }

  /* uniform label / value line */
  .line { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: baseline; padding: 4px 0; }
  .line .k {
    flex: none; width: 124px;
    font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px;
  }
  .line .v { font-size: 13px; color: var(--marble); line-height: 1.55; }
  .line .v i { font-style: normal; color: var(--bronze-light); padding: 0 3px; }
  .line .v b { color: #fff; font-weight: 600; }
  .line .v em { font-style: italic; color: var(--marble-dark); opacity: .8; }
  .line .v .muted { color: var(--marble-dark); opacity: .6; }

  /* resilience band — highlighted */
  .resil {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(201,168,76,.14), rgba(201,168,76,.04));
    border-top: 2px solid var(--bronze) !important;
  }
  .resil .dot {
    width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--gold);
    flex: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .line { flex-direction: column; gap: 3px; padding: 6px 0; }
    .line .k { width: auto; }
  }
</style>
